{"article_id":"AOL0YUrYYV8YImSF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Judge Puts Pennsylvania Voter ID Law On Hold Through Election","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A judge is basically `` postponing Pennsylvania 's tough new voter identification requirement ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"ordering","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"that it not be enforced in the presidential election , ''","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"The Associated Press writes .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"But in a ruling","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"that 's rather difficult to follow","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"if you 're not very familiar with the case ,","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"Commonwealth Court Judge Robert Simpson also says","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"he `` will not restrain election officials from asking for photo ID at the polls ;","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"rather , I will enjoin enforcement of those parts of Act 18","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"which directly result in disenfranchisement . ''","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Simpson ruled","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that a voter 's `` provisional ballot '' can not be declared invalid","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"because of the lack of an ID","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"and that the state 's transitional effort","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"to amend its laws","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"regarding such votes","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"must not take effect before Election Day","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"- Nov. 6 .","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"So ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"it appears from his ruling ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"election officials can ask for an ID .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"But a voter 's lack of one will not invalidate his vote .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"The ruling can be appealed to the state 's Supreme Court .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"`` Pennsylvania 's new law , among the toughest in the nation , is a signature accomplishment of Republicans in control of Pennsylvania state government","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"who say","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"they fear election fraud .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"But it is an emotional target for Democrats","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"who call it a Jim Crow-style scheme","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"to make it harder for their party 's traditional voters ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"including young adults and minorities ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"who might not carry the right kind of ID","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"or know about the law . ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Update at 10:20 a.m . ET .","depth":3},{"id":35,"text":"Bottom Line Is","depth":3},{"id":36,"text":"`` Pennsylvanians will not be required to show ID","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"to vote this year . '' `` Commonwealth Court Judge Robert Simpson has ruled","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"that Pennsylvanians will not be required to show ID","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"to vote this year .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"Simpson is postponing Pennsylvania 's tough new voter identification requirement ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"ordering","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that it not be enforced in the presidential election . ... `` The ruling means","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"people will be asked to show ID","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"but will be allowed to vote","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"even if they do n't .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"That was also the policy in effect for the primary this year . '' `` The injunction would have the effect","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"of extending the transition period of the law","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"- when voters were asked for identification","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"but could vote","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"without it -","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"through the November election . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":102,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":85,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":84,"right":34,"relation":"context","